Elevate Retirement

Salesforce is retiring the Elevate family of products. This affects Elevate Advanced Edition, Elevate Power of Us Editions, and all add-ons.
The ability to renew subscriptions will end on October 1, 2023, and the product will be deactivated on or after October 1, 2024.

Where: All Elevate products and editions.
